comments: Mrs. Nieto is a hands on teacher. She will go out of her way to assist her students. Very, very knowledgeable, she has a ton of history in her memory. Any subject she can relate and expand what\'s in the book. She made us think outside of the box and look at history through different perspective. She has a bucket list of must see movies and books.

To succeed in this course all you need to do is follow her instruction. She is very willing to answer questions and goes out of her way to help people get the information. Stay on top of the assignments and readings. Tests are multiple choices with like 4 short answer questions at the end.
